name: Crafting Crimes
summary:
Episode 2: The Wonderland Murders, now available!

Enter one of the bloodiest crime scenes ever recorded in Los Angeles’ history.

In 1981, four bodies were found inside a Hollywood home, exposing a tangled world of drugs, gangs, and nightlife. At the center of it all… a fallen adult film star who may be a witness, a suspect, or a scapegoat.
